product_name: Thule Gutter Foot Pack - Super High - Set of four
long_description: This is the ideal rack solution for vehicles with rain gutters. Perfect and secure fit even on very narrow gutters. Designed with vibration-damping, anti-slip vinyl coating. Galvanized, stamped steel construction with a black polyester powder-painted finish. Provides 11 inches of clearance above raingutter. Uses One Key System(TM) lock cylinders.
short_description: This is the ideal rack solution for vehicles with rain gutters.
